name: Devine Interlude
description:
It took me a while to find what I was looking for, 
But I believe I found it, The secret of life,
The crazy thing is - I lost everything I had in the process of searching for it,
But I’m glad I did, because I found the ultimate treasure,
I found the holy grail,
And I’m thankful,
I know who I am now and have something to stand for,
Hopefully this message will live on for generations to come,
And I pray that one day,
Each and every one of you may find yourselves too.
